  • Classes

    Description
    CarController
    Class that controls and updates all Car object properties such as their movement, sensors, collisions, etc.
    GameController
    Class to control the game logic such as the timer, the camera, initialization of the game objects, etc.
    GameControllerAI
    GameController child class that is used for AI controlled game mode to control the network visualizer and network of the cars.
    SpawnerController
    Class to spawn the enemy cars into the scene based on the level.
    VisualizerController
    Class to control the NeuralNetwork Visualizer.
